flowchart TD
    U[User] --> I[Input Request]
    I --> F[React Frontend]
    F --> API[Axios and REST API Calls]
    F --> SOC[Socket.IO Events]

    API --> B[Express Backend]
    SOC --> B

    B --> AUTH[Authentication Processing]
    B --> POST[Post Management]
    B --> USER[User Profile Management]
    B --> MSG[Message Handling]
    B --> ADM[Admin Operations]

    AUTH --> DB[(MongoDB)]
    POST --> DB
    USER --> DB
    MSG --> DB
    ADM --> DB

    DB --> B
    B --> O[Processed Response]
    O --> F
    F --> U
